<br>
Fastest way to learn is to stand near a fast zone line while someone spams you in group, when you get a point zone and zone back ( you have to be in the same zone to learn).<br>
<br>
Repeat for 1.5 hours and get to master.<br>
I suggest you turn group off so you are not visually spammed.<br>
<br>
Things to note.<br>
<br>
1. Learning is per line not per character<br>
2. Someone can only teach you to 1 point above there current skill<br>
3. Skill is level limited, you cannot get master until 19 (I think)<br>
